*Lost Sands Burglar: changed from 3/5 to 2/5
*Monsieur Scarlet: changed from 2/3 to 3/2
*Seedling King: changed from 5/4 to 4/3
*Shady Dealer: removed renew ability word (not a sorcery)
*Wasp Assault: added ability to hit planeswalkers
